♪The moonlight is as silent
as the deep sea♪

733
00:41:42,583 --> 00:41:45,043
♪From afar♪

734
00:41:46,993 --> 00:41:50,143
♪It once lit up dreams with a breath♪

735
00:41:51,063 --> 00:41:54,173
♪But vanished with a sigh♪

736
00:41:55,393 --> 00:41:58,763
♪Brushing past my fingertips♪

737
00:41:59,163 --> 00:42:02,533
♪My heartstrings were stirred quietly♪

738
00:42:03,363 --> 00:42:05,303
♪As if we once met before♪

739
00:42:05,793 --> 00:42:09,903
♪Holding back a love so deep♪

740
00:42:12,193 --> 00:42:15,563
♪Love asks for nothing in the end♪

741
00:42:16,153 --> 00:42:19,233
♪Leaving only obsessions♪

742
00:42:20,553 --> 00:42:23,953
♪I've wandered in the world♪

743
00:42:24,453 --> 00:42:27,453
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

744
00:42:29,013 --> 00:42:32,283
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

745
00:42:32,603 --> 00:42:36,293
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

746
00:42:36,993 --> 00:42:38,923
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

747
00:42:39,463 --> 00:42:44,383
♪How could I ever forget♪

748
00:42:44,963 --> 00:42:47,243
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

749
00:42:47,243 --> 00:42:49,763
♪To spend time with you♪

750
00:42:50,013 --> 00:42:51,373
♪When we grow old♪

751
00:42:51,373 --> 00:42:53,963
♪Nothing will change♪

752
00:42:53,963 --> 00:42:55,563
♪The misty rains never cease♪

753
00:42:55,563 --> 00:42:58,423
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

754
00:42:58,423 --> 00:43:02,413
♪Lingering in my heart♪

755
00:43:02,413 --> 00:43:04,113
♪I would sever fate's ties♪

756
00:43:04,113 --> 00:43:06,533
♪To protect your smiling eyes♪

757
00:43:06,923 --> 00:43:10,793
♪Even if behind me lies a storm♪

758
00:43:10,793 --> 00:43:11,903
♪No matter the trials♪

759
00:43:11,903 --> 00:43:15,123
♪I carry this longing for the journey♪

760
00:43:15,213 --> 00:43:17,203
♪This life♪

